<html>
<head>

</head>

<body>

<% if @email.to.split("@").last == "postif.com" %>

Mark,<br/><br/>

You got a new email from postif. It is from <%= @email.from %> and it is being sent to <%= @email.to %>.

<br/><br/>

<b>Subject:</b> <%= @email.subject %>

<br/>

<b>Message:</b><br/> 
<%= @email.message %>

<% else %>
Hi <%= @email.to %>,<br/><br/>

Your friend <%= @email.from %> wanted to tell you about <a href="http://www.postif.com">postif.com</a>!<br/><br/>

<div style="border:1px solid #CCCCCC; padding:10px; background:#EEEEEE">
<%= @email.message %>
</div>

<% end %>

<br/><br/>

<% if @email.to.split("@").last != "postif.com" %>
<table style='text-align:center; color:#668A3A;'>
  <tr>
    <td>"Got something you need to share?</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Instantly create a page on the web</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>with a link to share it!"</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
  <td><%= link_to image_tag('http://www.postif.com/images/logo.png'), 'http://www.postif.com' %></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<% end %>


</body>
</html>
